@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zzeltp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.64 / tmp + 0.45)) + (0.85 * v2))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.sin(v1 + 0.30)))
    v0 = 0.58
    v0 = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.95 + v0 + 0.39) / (v1 + 0.71 * tmp + 0.81)))
    v0 = 0.65
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.94) - ((v0 + 0.17 / v1 + 0.52) + wp.cos(v2 + 0.97)))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
